{"tid":711183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋男攞手錶郵包　藏13萬元K仔","createTime":"2018-06-21T10:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:49:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8cafe0656dc392db8ccfef01e2c60dccc8d6fb3e","tid":711183,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180621/20427225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F20427225&d=5eA8betqB0%2BzXbXhkNI%2F154f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b9c97b7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F20427225&h=96a24d04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180621/20427225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月21日 <br />\n<br />\n公屋男攞手錶郵包　藏13萬元K仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海關機場空運貨物組，上星期六截查一個由馬來西亞寄港空運郵包，郵包報稱寄運手錶，但關員發現郵包內只有一個膠盒，內有約250克懷疑氯胺酮(K仔)，市值約13萬元。<br />\n<br />\n海關毒品調查科接手，根據郵包收件地址，前日在深水埗富昌邨，拘捕一名29歲、報稱任雜工的本地男子，涉嫌販運危險藥物，正追緝毒品來源，又重申販運危險藥物屬刑事罪行，一經定罪，最高可被判處罰款500萬元及終身監禁。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n5部門深水埗洗太平地　破武器庫拉17人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【動畫】女鐵騎自炒倒地　暖男單車護花"},{"pid":"0c8ea5d0f0f5222f201542309faf0a41fb7b4dd3","tid":711183,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:49:04.000Z","msg":"住公屋咁有錢都運毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}